				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The way I did it was in this format:<br /><br />word 0: 0 = exit routine, 1 = small sprite, 2 = big sprite<br />word 1: x displacement<br />word 2: y displacement<br />word 3: name and attributes<br /><br />I use 16-bit words because it is difficult to check bounds and finding the 9th x-bit, using 8 bits.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

